d，方可使用此功能繳付續保費用及徵費。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年5月1 日起，只接受以香港境外簽發的VISA / MasterCard登記繳費。</span></strong><br />\n只有成功登記之信用卡才能用作網上繳費。<br />\n您亦可登記多於一張信用卡作繳費之用。<br />\n信用卡持有人必須為保單持有人本人。<br />\n如使用香港簽發的VISA / MasterCard信用卡繳費，只接受以已登記的信用卡繳付於2020年5月1日前生效的保單的續保費用。<br />\n若保單是透過渣打銀行（香港）有限公司投保，則只接受以渣打 / Manhattan (VISA / MasterCard)信用卡繳付續保費用。<br />\n每宗成功以香港境外簽發的VISA / 萬事達卡的網上繳費交易須繳付付款金額的2.8%的海外付款行政費，而該行政費或於保費退款時不被退還。此外，個別銀行預設的單筆交易限額及日累計交易限額有所分別，請自行與銀行查詢詳情。"},{"pid":"1f751d0a01f058940618efe1ee8dd6ddbf821192","tid":1994441,"uid":76591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"54d901692a7bbedf181bb8902bdacc469ddf281d","tid":1994441,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"quote":{"pid":"e14453a33b6c0189a2c4299a0030531c5ce1f9c9","tid":1994441,"uid":51711,"like":291,"dislike":2,"score":289,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"抖陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"國際版黎ga"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"SSR... 抖音...<br />\n你住大陸架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c13bd4cffc47b726454cc523f0de954593706c4","tid":1994441,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"仲你老母<br />\n做同仲個音爭勁遠囉屌你"},{"pid":"32d433e05f905b2e67926774875d8a9d09856da4","tid":1994441,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62940d2a37495d9169949958896bcf66ced4d1a4","tid":1994441,"uid":277124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8f22eed0e5bc5f8c6d407a388aca38d35a0c56","tid":1994441,"uid":94494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:47:48.000Z","msg":"Del左個抹音先出post啦"},{"pid":"d2a3862e7b721cb84395db97732e59160b042ebd","tid":1994441,"uid"